Tue Feb 20 17:16:33 GMT+1 2001  Andreas Bauer  <baueran@users.berlios.de>

 - Fixed up problems with wrong doc/ and pixmap/ paths affecting mostly
   the RPM versions though


Sun Feb 18 12:28:14 GMT+1 2001  Andreas Bauer  <baueran@users.berlios.de>

 - Fixed --gnoscanrc switch so the creation of rcfiles can be implemented now

 - Added automatic creation of new rcfiles

 - Added scanning of entire subnets by defining a netmask


Thu Feb 15 12:00:21 GMT+1 2001  Andreas Bauer  <baueran@users.berlios.de>

 - Added multi-threaded port scan

 - Added gthread support to configure.in

 - Added more dynamic paths to help file and scan button pixmap


